	<td>
	    <br>
	    <font size=3>
	    
	    <a href="http://www.brill.com/intranet/">The Intranet Journal</a><br>
	    A great site for Intranet related information. Check out the links
	    area<br>for some cool Intranet software companies.<br>
	    <p>		
        
	    <a href="http://home.netscape.com/comprod/at_work/index.html">Intranet Solutions</a><br>
	    Netscapes Intranet solutions page.<br>
	    <p>		

