        <td valign="top">The National Alliance for the Mentally Ill&#146;s Campaign

        to End Discrimination is dedicated to erasing the stigma associated

        with brain disorders. Unfortunately, negative stereotypes

        and misconceptions about mental illnesses still exist. However,

        the StigmaBusting Network is taking measures to end the stigma

        surrounding brain disorders.</td>

