<p align="left">We are getting the message out that stigma and

discrimination will no longer be tolerated. And our voice will be

even louder with the help of you. Write to companies guilty of using negative stereotypes. Send

NAMI examples of stigma to, attention: StigmaBusting Network. You

will automatically become part of our growing and newly revised StigmaBusting

Network. As a member, you will receive periodic stigma alerts

asking you to take part in a grassroots campaign to fight stigma. </p>

<div align="center"><center>



<pre><b>StigmaBusting Network

200 N. Glebe Rd.  #1015

Arlington, VA  22203

Sarah@nami.org 

</b></pre>

</center></div>



<p align="center"><em><strong>We look forward to hearing from

you!</strong></em></p>



