<p>2 - suffered from bipolar 
depression </p>
<p>3 - discussed in 
<u>Dynamics of Creation</u> by 
Anthony Storr &amp; in 
<u>Creative Malady</u> by 
George Pickering</p>
</blockquote>
<p><font color="#FF0000">Leo Tolstoy </font></p>
<blockquote>
<p>1 - author </p>
<p>2 - revealed his own 
mental illness in <u>My 
Confession</u> </p>
<p>3 - discussed in 
<u>Dynamics of Creation</u> by 
Anthony Storr &amp; in <u>Inner 
World of Madness</u> by 
Bert Kaplan </p>
</blockquote>
<p><font color="#FF0000">Vaslov Nijinsky </font></p>
<blockquote>
<p>1 - dancer </p>
<p>2 - suffered from clinical 
depression </p>
<p>3 - documented in his 
autobiography The Diary 
of Vaslov Nijinsky </p>
<p>4 - documented in <u>Inner 
World of Madness</u> by 
Bert Kaplan &amp; in <i>U.S. 
News &amp; World Report</i></p>
</blockquote>
<p><font color="#FF0000">John Keats </font></p>
