Broken Brain</u> by Nancy 
Andreasen</p>
</blockquote>
<p><font color="#FF0000">Edgar Allan Poe </font></p>
<blockquote>
<p>1 - author/poet </p>
<p>2 - suffered from bipolar 
depression </p>
<p>3 - documented in <u>The 
Haunted Palace: The Life 
of Edgar Allan Poe</u> by 
Frances Winwar</p>
</blockquote>
