<DOCHDR>
http://www.nami.org:80/helpline/whatdiss.htm 38.250.129.71 19970222105145 text/html 6860
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sat, 22 Feb 1997 10:50:13 GMT
Server: Apache/1.0.5
