<DOCHDR>
http://www.nami.org:80/helpline/effexor.htm 38.250.129.71 19970222105408 text/html 7363
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sat, 22 Feb 1997 10:52:32 GMT
Server: Apache/1.0.5
Content-type: text/html
