                <td><a href="/"><img src="nami.gif"
                alt="NAMI Home Page" border="0" width="150"
                height="45"></a> </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        </td>
        <td valign="top"><h2 align="center"><font color="#0000FF"
        size="4">Recent Media Coverage</font></h2>
<hr>
        <p align="left">NAMI monitors media coverage on a wide
        range of topics related to severe mental illnesses or
        brain disorders, such as schizophrenia, bipolar disorder
        (manic-depressive illness), clinical depression, or
        anxiety disorders. </p>
        <p align="left">As an information resource to media
        representatives, we have compiled a listing that provides
        the dates, titles, reporters, and media outlets for
        articles that have been printed or stories aired
        recently. This listing, which is routinely updated, is
        only a sampling of recent media coverage. It is not an
        exhaustive catalogue. </p>
        <ul>
            <li><p align="left"><a href="/pressroom/media/recentall.htm">Media Monitor</a> (for entire
                listing)</p>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <blockquote>
            <ul>
                <li><p align="left"><a href="/pressroom/media/child.htm">Children &amp; Adolescents</a> </p>
                </li>
                <li><p align="left"><a href="/pressroom/media/insurance.htm">Health Insurance</a> </p>
                </li>
                <li><p align="left"><a href="/pressroom/media/housing.htm">Homelessness/Housing</a> </p>
                </li>
                <li><p align="left"><a href="/pressroom/media/legal.htm">Legal/Criminal Justice System</a>
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li><p align="left"><a href="/pressroom/media/hmo.htm">Managed Care/HMOs</a> </p>
                </li>
                <li><p align="left"><a href="/pressroom/media/medicare.htm">Medicare/Medicaid</a> </p>
                </li>
                <li><p align="left"><a href="/pressroom/media/personal.htm">Personal Stories</a> </p>
                </li>
                <li><p align="left"><a href="/pressroom/media/research.htm">Research</a> </p>
                </li>
                <li><p align="left"><a href="/pressroom/media/treatment.htm">Treatment</a> </p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </blockquote>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>

