Pharmaceuticals, Inc.</i></strong></font></p>



<p align="center"><font color="#008000" size="3"><strong><i>Pfizer,

Inc.</i></strong></font></p>



<p align="center"><font color="#008000" size="3"><strong><i>Sandoz

Pharmaceuticals</i></strong></font></p>



<p align="center"><font color="#008000" size="3"><strong><i>SmithKline

Beecham</i></strong></font></p>



<p align="center"><font color="#008000" size="3"><strong><i>Wyeth-Ayerst

Laboratories</i></strong></font></p>



<p align="center"><font color="#008000" size="3"><i>&nbsp;</i></font></p>



