<H1><STRONG>Maryland News</STRONG></H1>
<IMG SRC="gif/line_blu.gif"><BR>
</CENTER>
<BR>





<IMG SRC="gif/bul_bl_r.gif" ALT="[*]"><A HREF="#Managed Care">Putting Care Into Managed Care
Part II Conference</A><EM>(Fall '96)</EM><BR>
<IMG SRC="gif/bul_bl_r.gif" ALT="[*]"><A HREF="#Medicaid">Medicaid Waiver Passes:  What will It Mean?</A><EM>(Summer '96)</EM><BR>
