<H2>New Brochures Replace "Mood Disorders"</H2>
<hr>



	NAMI's two new brochures--Understanding Major Depression:  What You Need To Know About This Medical Illness(item R005) and Understanding Manic Depression:  What You Need To Know About This Medical Illness(item R006)--have replaced the brochure, Mood Disorders (item R102, which is no longer available).  The two new brochures can be ordered from the NAMI RDS bookstore, and they are 20 cents per copy.  For more information, call the bookstore at 703/524-7600.

